@database FM
@remark $VER: VHI-FMdriver.guide 1.25

@node MAIN
@title "VHI-FrameMachine driver"

                   @{b}VHI FrameMachine driver@{ub}

   A driver for the VHI-interface for the electronic-design
                   FrameMachine video card.


  @{b}*** To use this driver, you also need to download the ***
  ***     latest FMdriver-package which contains the    ***
  ***            FrameMachine hardware driver!!!        ***@{ub}

  The FMdriver-package also contains a full documentation of
  this new FrameMachine driver system.

  To get the FMdriver-package and the latest VHI-driver version,
  please visit my homepage:

  @{b}http://www.qdev.de@{ub}

  You find there much more interesting FrameMachine programs and
  other cool stuff...


